text: Kalshali () is a rural locality (a selo) in Karamaly-Gubeyevsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 525 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 43 km from Tuymazy, 4 km from Karamaly-Gubeyevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Kalshali
